prompts.frontCover:
Minimalist greeting card front, 2D flat illustration, clean elegant style. Two characters are sitting on a San Diego beach towel on pale sand. In the background are simple, iconic San Diego beach elements: stylized rolling ocean waves in shades of blue and a minimalist sun setting on the horizon.

The character Lao Lao from the photo (on the left) is depicted as a cartoon, sitting with a happy, laughing expression. She is wearing her light blue sweatshirt and black pants. She is gleefully slurping from an oversized boba tea cup with a giant straw.

The character Jordan from the photo (on the right) is depicted as a cartoon, wearing his tan hoodie and dark pants. He is looking at Lao Lao with a funny, exasperated expression as he gets playfully smacked in the face by a giant, rogue boba pearl flying out of Lao Lao's cup. The boba pearl is mid-air, comically large, with a small motion trail.

Centered in the space above the characters, the greeting "Happy Birthday Lao Lao" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script in a dark teal color. The overall composition is humorous, lighthearted, and has a clean, minimalist aesthetic with a soft pastel color palette. --ar 5:7 --style raw
